

<section class="app-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Event Management App</h1>
    <p class="description">
      This Event Management App is a simple and efficient platform for creating, viewing, updating, and deleting events.
      Built using the MERN stack, it helps users manage events with ease.
    </p>

    <div class="features">
      <h2>Core Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Create Events:</strong> Add event title, date, time, and description.</li>
        <li><strong>View Events:</strong> See a list of all events with their details.</li>
        <li><strong>Update Events:</strong> Edit existing event information anytime.</li>
        <li><strong>Delete Events:</strong> Remove events that are no longer needed.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="tech">
      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Frontend:</strong> EJS, HTML, CSS<br/>
        <strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js<br/>
        <strong>Database:</strong> MongoDB with Mongoose
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="usage">
      <h2>How to Use</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Go to the event dashboard.</li>
        <li>Click on “Create Event” to add a new event.</li>
        <li>Edit or delete events from the event list.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      <p>This is a basic CRUD app and can be extended with user login, reminders, or RSVP features.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


